        <h1 class="acl-title">European Union — AI Copyright Law</h1>
        <p class="acl-excerpt">The EU balances AI innovation with creator rights through the AI Act's transparency mandates and the DSM Directive's structured Text and Data Mining (TDM) exceptions.</p>
      </div>
